Package: dspline
Title: Tools for computations with discrete splines
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
   person("Addison", "Hu", 
           role = "aut"),
   person("Ryan", "Tibshirani", 
          role = c("aut", "cre"),
          email = "ryantibs@gmail.com"))
Description: This package provides tools for computations relating to discrete
    splines, such as discrete differentiation and integration, various matrix 
		computations with discrete derivative or discrete spline bases matrices, and 
		interpolation within discrete spline spaces.  
